How to install Visual Studio Code onto Your Computer

To install VS Code, you'll want to visit their website to get the appropriate installer for your operating system. Make sure 
you visit the VS Code website, and not the Visual Studio website.

For Windows, you can download an EXE installer. Once you're downloaded it, run the file and the setup wizard will take you
through the installation process.

